## Basic Information
This file contains the emission-line fits from Spectro-1D.  A best-fit
stellar absorption-line template has been subtracted.

### Naming Convention
spZline- <i>pppp</i> - <i>mmmmm</i> .fits

### Releases
DR9, DR10, DR12, DR11, DR13, DR14, DR15, DR16, DR17

### Enviroments
BOSS_SPECTRO_REDUX

### Approximate Size
20 MB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
migration: not in database. Needs update

### HDU List for release DR17
  - [HDU0: PRIMARY](#hdu0-primary)
  - [HDU1: ](#hdu1-)
  - [HDU2: ](#hdu2-)
